===================
Version 44.0~alpha1
===================
* Port to GTK4 and libadwaita
* Rework prefs using mobile friendly widgets
* Fix PKINIT with Heimdal Kerberos
* Update examples to use Python3
* Cleanup and simplify (dropping ~1000 LOC)

============
